OL,4,G1300FDanger Man
OL,5,     GAfter receiving a death sentence
OL,6,     Gabroad, American James Carpenter
OL,7,     Ghas spent five years hiding in a
OL,8,     GU.S. embassy. Agent John Drake
OL,9,     Gmust secretly get him out of the
OL,10,     Gcountry safely before time runs
OL,11,     Gout.
OL,12,G1330FDanger Man
OL,13,     GJohn Drake trails a foreign agent
OL,14,     Gto Kashmir, hoping to discover
OL,15,     Ghow he is passing secret
OL,16,     Ginformation out of the country.
OL,17,     GHe discovers the agent's contact
OL,18,     Gto be a woman named Louise
OL,19,     GGoddard.
